 ~/t.modpar313      change module 313 parameters
 5         /change module parameters
 4,4       /box size
 1,1       /width height of nodes without node number
 0         /offset to right for links
 4         /character height
 y         /plot only if connected
 999999    /hatch width
 y         /save on disk
 6         /end
 9         /end emme2
